ErrorPagesGenerator
===================

Generates static 404.html and 500.html error pages using your layouts.

Alternatives
===========

http://blog.ubrio.us/code/rails-22-custom-error-pages-with-exception-loggable/
http://m.onkey.org/2008/7/20/rescue-from-dispatching

Example
=======

rake generate_error_pages


